revision.text:
The Togakushi shrine is a shrine on a mountain near [[Togakushi, Nagano|Togakushi]], [[Nagano prefecture|Nagano]], [[Japan]]. The Shrine is also part of the in the [[Joshinetsu Kogen National Park]]. The shrine is also known for its natural beauty, especially the approach up the mountain lined with majestic old cedar trees.
==See also==
*[[List of Shinto shrines]]

